{"tid":2078506,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國務院報告指港府錯誤把民主人權抗爭視為恐怖主義","createTime":"2020-06-25T05:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T11:57:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4ef9d4e5ce0b286bc535470dbd9cf0b377433843","tid":2078506,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/119342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F119342&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2Qfe%2FcXzH0lQqBACTLtzCSRXY%3D&h=d99130a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/119342</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發表2019年反恐報告，在香港部分，報告說香港在2019年沒有恐襲報告。報告說，香港當局在去年錯誤地將民主和人權抗議者的行為視為恐怖主義。中國駐香港發言人將示威者的行為描述為恐怖主義苗頭，亦屬於錯誤。報告又說，中國政府繼續以對抗所謂極端主義為幌子，在新疆實施鎮壓運動。當局加強了對維吾爾人和其他穆斯林進行大規模「再教育」或「職業培訓」，但美國政府認為實際目標是鎮壓極端主義，宗教和少數民族。美國國務院認為，中國政府對恐怖主義和極端主義的廣泛定義，以及對網絡恐怖主義的模糊定義，繼續引起對人權的嚴重關注。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-25 13:40:25"},{"pid":"36cdb896d4ec7c78b3a21373974286227bbd409a","tid":2078506,"uid":273703,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:53:30.000Z","msg":"佢地準備將香港變新疆，絕對唔係錯誤而係借鑒"},{"pid":"9b36fa61827291de2c253c50e94554bd19a152b0","tid":2078506,"uid":200318,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yyWxUsS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyyWxUsS.gif&h=048c49f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d825f03e4d0a626939f94c71963015eef8568c6a","tid":2078506,"uid":132587,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:55:09.000Z","msg":"唔係錯誤<br />\n係擺明老屈<br />\n幫國安法鋪路<br />\n屈人整炸彈整子彈 收埋真槍<br />\n全部等到國安法過左先告"},{"pid":"b4faf954487271cae60cf8772afcca88e2ea1b7a","tid":2078506,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:55:14.000Z","msg":"Thank you America<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07c7ceb916d27d57a7f301bb02bae60e456c3c